README:

1.) Copy all wikipad.* files to a location that can not be accessed remotely.
2.) Install https://hg.nhg.name/unchroot/
3.) Configure wikipad.conf.phs and make sure that all paths are accessible.
4.) Configure CRON to call wikipad.phs regularly:
    */5 * * * * root php /path/to/wikipad.phs >/dev/null 2>&1
